Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.70,0:25:00.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sledeći put na Melanholiji Suzumije Haruhi:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.78,0:25:01.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Epizoda devet!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.56,0:25:01.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Greška.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.93,0:25:03.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Utuvi više to u glavu.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.25,0:25:04.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sledeći put na Melanholiji Suzumije Haruhi:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.70,0:25:05.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Epizoda šest...
